S.FORM: Denmark Gaga kska Owcow ka Denmark, 56 00 N, 10 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 43,094 sq km(hangan na o Tg134)(knlbanga dxgal o 42,434 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 660 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 5,593,785 hiyi. Gaga Copenhagen ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 5 idas 6 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Denmark ga wada sugan 63.40 ka dxgal qpahan, 12.90 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 23.70 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Frederik X, pnaah hngkawas2024 idas 1 jiyax 14pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
